WEBVTT

01:32.150 --> 01:33.870
Oh, Qiao Qingyu.

01:34.150 --> 01:36.020
Seeing you reminds me of something.

01:36.020 --> 01:37.900
A few days ago, I saw Ming Sheng

01:37.900 --> 01:39.539
getting out of a cab with a girl.

01:39.539 --> 01:40.750
Was it you?

01:42.270 --> 01:43.910
Was she staying

01:43.950 --> 01:45.660
at Ming Sheng's grandpa's?

01:46.020 --> 01:47.660
They're quite close.

01:47.660 --> 01:48.820
Don't make things up.

01:51.020 --> 01:51.590
She was staying

01:51.590 --> 01:53.500
with our distant relative.

01:54.310 --> 01:55.740
So just mind

01:55.780 --> 01:56.590
your own business.

01:57.460 --> 01:59.190
I'm not making things up.

01:59.190 --> 02:00.270
I remember clearly

02:00.270 --> 02:01.780
what she was wearing that day.

02:01.780 --> 02:02.140
She...

02:02.270 --> 02:03.630
Mom, you're back.

02:03.660 --> 02:05.020
Let's go home.

02:05.380 --> 02:06.190
Come on.

02:16.140 --> 02:17.270
Why are you back too?

02:18.060 --> 02:19.020
Get me some water.

02:19.780 --> 02:21.100
I forgot to bring my cleats.

02:21.140 --> 02:22.510
The teacher wouldn't let me
join the class,

02:22.510 --> 02:23.510
so I had to come back and fetch them.

02:23.630 --> 02:25.230
You're always so forgetful.

02:25.420 --> 02:27.270
Make sure
you haven't left anything behind

02:27.500 --> 02:28.700
so you don't have to

02:28.910 --> 02:30.420
keep running back and forth.

02:36.700 --> 02:37.829
I'll leave the keys here.

02:37.990 --> 02:38.940
I'm heading back to the noodle house.

02:39.829 --> 02:40.990
Remember to lock the door
from the outside.

02:41.500 --> 02:42.190
All right, Mom.

02:42.190 --> 02:43.270
Bring me the keys later.

02:43.940 --> 02:44.750
Okay.

02:45.740 --> 02:48.160
[If you turn around,
I'll always be there.]

02:57.940 --> 02:58.630
Jinyu.

02:58.670 --> 02:59.190
What?

03:00.140 --> 03:01.300
Do me a favor.

03:01.420 --> 03:02.630
I need to go out.

03:04.110 --> 03:06.190
Where are you going?

03:06.390 --> 03:07.990
Mom won't spare me if she finds out.

03:08.300 --> 03:09.470
I need to see Ming Sheng.

03:15.340 --> 03:16.030
Qingyu,

03:16.390 --> 03:17.340
what has happened

03:17.550 --> 03:18.990
between you and Ming Sheng?

03:19.470 --> 03:22.579
The owner of the grocery downstairs

03:22.829 --> 03:25.470
has been coming

03:25.470 --> 03:26.829
to the noodle house

03:26.829 --> 03:28.550
and keeping gossiping to Mom

03:28.829 --> 03:30.579
about you and Ming Sheng.

03:31.460 --> 03:32.390
Ignore her.

03:32.550 --> 03:34.350
If she comes again, drive her away.

03:35.140 --> 03:36.300
If we get on her nerves,

03:36.300 --> 03:37.510
won't she

03:37.510 --> 03:39.230
go around insulting us?

03:40.020 --> 03:40.990
Mom said

03:41.340 --> 03:44.180
the leases for both the noodle house
and this apartment are for one year.

03:44.620 --> 03:45.990
When September comes,

03:46.180 --> 03:47.270
we'll move out.

03:48.070 --> 03:50.020
Next year,

03:50.420 --> 03:51.990
when you graduate,

03:52.230 --> 03:53.790
you'll be studying elsewhere.

03:53.829 --> 03:56.620
I'll be staying here in Huanzhou
to finish my studies.

03:57.140 --> 03:59.020
Mom and Dad will move back to Shunyun.

03:59.020 --> 04:01.140
It'll help them out a lot financially.

04:03.350 --> 04:06.140
What happened
between you and Ming Sheng?

04:11.300 --> 04:12.460
Nothing.

04:12.990 --> 04:14.790
Then why were you at his place?

04:17.070 --> 04:18.740
It's hard to explain.

04:18.860 --> 04:20.510
But I must see him today,

04:21.510 --> 04:23.830
and I won't have anything to do
with him after this.

04:27.580 --> 04:31.420
Well, you make me do this.

04:32.390 --> 04:33.180
Since you didn't

04:33.620 --> 04:36.390
make a fuss about me taking something

04:36.390 --> 04:37.990
from the drawer last time,

04:38.390 --> 04:39.350
I will do you

04:39.700 --> 04:40.700
this favor.

04:40.990 --> 04:42.700
But if you want to see Ming Sheng,

04:42.700 --> 04:44.180
you need to tell him first.

04:44.950 --> 04:46.950
I have to send the keys back to Mom.

04:47.510 --> 04:49.230
We only have

04:49.230 --> 04:51.300
two hours tops.

04:52.990 --> 04:53.790
That's more than enough.

04:54.180 --> 04:55.990
I'm going to the internet cafe
to text him.

04:56.900 --> 04:59.180
Are you sure he'll come?

05:00.700 --> 05:01.510
I hope so.

05:06.940 --> 05:08.460
[Episode 15]

05:08.460 --> 05:11.840
[Meet You At the Tree]

05:28.640 --> 05:31.040
[Qingyu: Meet you at the tree. Now.]

06:16.470 --> 06:17.350
You ruined my leaf.

06:18.150 --> 06:19.350
This isn't yours.

06:20.470 --> 06:21.910
This is my tree.

06:25.150 --> 06:26.710
Actually, the tree can talk.

06:27.790 --> 06:28.790
It's saying...

06:31.820 --> 06:33.500
I shouldn't have
lost my temper with you yesterday.

06:34.820 --> 06:35.790
Sorry.

07:11.180 --> 07:13.030
I heard your mom's been keeping
a close eye on you.

07:13.350 --> 07:14.860
Didn't expect you'd get out so soon.

07:16.380 --> 07:18.180
My mom says if you keep coming to me,

07:18.420 --> 07:19.860
she'll set your house on fire.

07:20.300 --> 07:21.670
She's not joking.

07:23.350 --> 07:24.820
But I think it's kind of funny.

07:25.300 --> 07:27.710
She acted like there was
really something between us.

07:29.300 --> 07:30.670
If it weren't for your mom,

07:31.350 --> 07:32.420
I wouldn't know

07:32.940 --> 07:34.710
I mattered so much to you.

07:35.740 --> 07:36.860
Don't talk nonsense.

07:39.060 --> 07:40.060
I'm not.

07:42.940 --> 07:44.180
Since you've read the note

07:45.710 --> 07:46.820
and asked to meet me,

07:47.670 --> 07:49.180
shouldn't you explain

07:50.260 --> 07:51.710
why you left without a word?

07:58.060 --> 07:58.940
What makes you think

07:58.940 --> 08:01.150
I'd choose you over my family?

08:05.150 --> 08:06.940
You're more eager to leave home
than I am.

08:07.790 --> 08:09.740
This is only a game to you.

08:12.740 --> 08:13.550
You're right.

08:13.910 --> 08:15.550
I'm willing to risk my future

08:16.670 --> 08:18.030
and everything for this game.

08:22.150 --> 08:23.380
I asked to meet you today

08:23.380 --> 08:25.860
because there are some things
I want to tell you in person.

08:27.180 --> 08:29.180
I appreciate everything
you've done for me,

08:30.380 --> 08:32.470
but there's never been anything

08:33.419 --> 08:36.419
between us,

08:37.470 --> 08:38.740
and there never will be.

08:43.110 --> 08:44.110
I don't understand.

08:48.990 --> 08:50.470
There's no future for us.

08:51.350 --> 08:52.710
What do you mean?

08:54.990 --> 08:57.230
After graduation, you'll be overseas,

08:57.230 --> 08:58.500
and I'll stay here.

08:59.110 --> 09:00.990
Our lives have always been going
in different directions.

09:01.110 --> 09:02.620
It's just how it is.

09:03.710 --> 09:04.860
You have your future,

09:05.740 --> 09:06.910
and I won't stand in your way.

09:08.260 --> 09:09.380
I managed to help you

09:09.380 --> 09:10.670
even when I was abroad, didn't I?

09:11.030 --> 09:12.590
When you were at the station
during the Chinese New Year,

09:12.590 --> 09:13.180
you were burning up.

09:13.180 --> 09:14.420
Wasn't I the one who came fetch you?

09:14.620 --> 09:16.230
I'll decide what my future is.

09:16.230 --> 09:17.670
But I'm not like you.

09:17.910 --> 09:19.350
The moment I was taken back,

09:19.350 --> 09:20.180
I lost.

09:20.180 --> 09:21.670
I can't hurt my family again,

09:21.670 --> 09:23.550
and I can't run away from home
a second time.

09:25.150 --> 09:26.500
Just ignore me

09:26.500 --> 09:27.820
or treat me as someone you dislike,

09:27.820 --> 09:29.180
like you did last term.

09:29.180 --> 09:30.420
I didn't ignore you

09:30.420 --> 09:31.620
or dislikef you.

09:31.620 --> 09:32.820
But my life would've been much easier

09:32.820 --> 09:34.420
without you.

09:37.230 --> 09:38.420
You're a burden to me.

09:43.260 --> 09:44.910
I've hated you from the beginning.

09:45.300 --> 09:47.350
I thought you were egoistic
and arrogant.

09:47.350 --> 09:49.060
You walked over me as you like.

09:49.350 --> 09:50.710
Even though my life is terrible enough,

09:50.710 --> 09:52.060
we don't belong in the same world.

09:57.830 --> 09:58.740
Qiao Qingyu.

10:02.140 --> 10:04.020
I never meant to hurt you.

10:05.950 --> 10:06.950
I'm sorry.

10:12.590 --> 10:14.230
It's fine
if you don't accept my apology.

10:15.430 --> 10:16.260
But could you please

10:17.740 --> 10:18.710
not hate me?

10:28.900 --> 10:29.900
I hate you.

10:58.380 --> 10:59.190
Qiao Qingyu.

11:02.350 --> 11:04.740
I used to think we had a lot in common.

11:06.740 --> 11:07.660
However,

11:09.020 --> 11:10.190
I was wrong.

11:14.190 --> 11:15.310
What would you choose?

11:16.860 --> 11:18.190
I'd choose freedom.

11:18.380 --> 11:19.900
Why would one live

11:21.350 --> 11:22.590
without freedom?

11:33.230 --> 11:34.020
Qiao Qingyu.

11:37.780 --> 11:39.310
Are we still friends?

11:50.110 --> 11:52.540
It's fine. Never mind.

12:00.990 --> 12:01.860
Ming Sheng.

12:04.860 --> 12:07.140
I'm very grateful to you
for everything you did.

12:15.350 --> 12:16.540
It's pointless

12:19.380 --> 12:20.310
to say that now.

12:23.190 --> 12:23.990
Just go.

12:23.990 --> 12:27.440
♪Turns out that what's on your mind♪

12:27.780 --> 12:31.810
♪Is a place♪

12:32.230 --> 12:37.520
♪Where the same story is held dear♪

12:38.280 --> 12:41.550
♪Fortunately, I'm not sensible enough♪

12:42.100 --> 12:45.280
♪Courage wasn't late too♪

12:45.860 --> 12:51.990
♪Only then does time
not betray our acquaintance♪

13:14.860 --> 13:16.660
Every choice in life

13:17.110 --> 13:19.500
is a battle with oneself.

13:20.710 --> 13:22.140
The worst feeling

13:22.430 --> 13:24.020
isn't when others deny you

13:24.660 --> 13:26.110
but when you doubt yourself.

13:41.140 --> 13:43.430
The world of my inner self
suddenly collapses.

13:45.140 --> 13:46.740
I feel that I've never

13:46.740 --> 13:48.860
truly connected with this world.

13:50.260 --> 13:51.710
Everything around me is in chaos,

13:52.380 --> 13:54.540
like I'm surrounded by a thick fog.

13:55.830 --> 13:57.900
Even though my body grows as it should,

13:58.950 --> 14:01.190
my soul feels lost.

14:18.320 --> 14:21.650
[Huanzhou High School Grade 2, Class 5.
Monthly Test Results]

14:25.020 --> 14:26.070
Guan Lan,

14:26.230 --> 14:28.500
I'm only one point

14:28.620 --> 14:31.070
and one rank behind you in class,

14:31.230 --> 14:34.140
but in the whole grade,
I'm 20 spots behind you.

14:35.020 --> 14:37.140
Now I understand what Sun meant

14:37.140 --> 14:38.860
about how much difference
one point can make in NCEE.

14:38.860 --> 14:39.990
Coming through.

14:40.260 --> 14:42.540
Why are you so excited, Ye Zilin?

14:42.540 --> 14:44.430
You're always at the bottom of the list.

14:44.500 --> 14:46.430
I'm checking for Sheng.

14:47.110 --> 14:48.990
Well done. 14th place.

14:50.020 --> 14:52.110
Full marks in Biology and Physics.

14:52.110 --> 14:53.430
What has happened to Ming Sheng?

14:53.430 --> 14:54.620
Why didn't he turn in
blank answer sheets this time?

14:54.620 --> 14:56.620
He's either scoring zero
or perfect scores in papers.

14:56.620 --> 14:58.500
That's a real skill, you know?

14:59.350 --> 15:00.900
Oh, Qiao Qingyu is the 13th.

15:01.500 --> 15:02.590
13 and 14.

15:03.380 --> 15:05.260
Doesn't that mean
they will always be together?

15:06.140 --> 15:06.540
Tsk.

15:08.950 --> 15:11.500
Sheng, look at this.

15:11.830 --> 15:12.710
Is it funny?

15:14.110 --> 15:15.110
Is it not?

15:24.310 --> 15:25.190
Not funny?

15:25.660 --> 15:26.660
Be together.

15:27.380 --> 15:28.260
Not really.

15:46.260 --> 15:47.070
Qingyu.

15:49.430 --> 15:50.350
Mr. Sun.

15:53.070 --> 15:53.950
Mr. Pan told me

15:54.830 --> 15:56.140
about your essay.

15:56.430 --> 15:57.350
I never imagined

15:57.780 --> 15:59.780
a quiet girl like you

16:00.110 --> 16:01.740
would have such a secret.

16:04.740 --> 16:05.540
To be frank,

16:06.230 --> 16:08.310
I went through something similar.

16:09.020 --> 16:11.500
I suddenly realized
those generally accepted values

16:11.740 --> 16:13.140
and principles in life

16:13.350 --> 16:14.830
weren't right.

16:15.540 --> 16:16.990
It made me uncomfortable

16:17.260 --> 16:18.190
because I wasn't sure

16:18.190 --> 16:19.190
whether the problem was with me

16:19.190 --> 16:20.540
or the world.

16:21.380 --> 16:23.020
But later, I began to understand

16:23.350 --> 16:25.620
these rules aren't written in stone.

16:25.620 --> 16:26.590
It all depends.

16:27.780 --> 16:30.260
For example, hiding the truth

16:31.590 --> 16:32.860
isn't necessarily wrong.

16:33.110 --> 16:34.350
It depends on the reason behind it.

16:35.660 --> 16:38.190
I think the best way to grow

16:38.190 --> 16:39.990
is to face life
with restraint and gentleness.

16:40.620 --> 16:42.710
The things that once brought you pain

16:42.900 --> 16:44.350
will fade

16:44.590 --> 16:45.740
with time.

16:46.190 --> 16:49.020
We experience so much
and meet so many people

16:49.260 --> 16:50.350
every day.

16:50.950 --> 16:53.070
They're beyond
our prediction or control.

16:53.070 --> 16:54.710
Don't struggle

16:54.710 --> 16:56.020
but face it all with a smile.

16:56.660 --> 16:58.110
[Psychological Health]
The school has invited

16:58.110 --> 16:59.540
[Education and Counseling Center]
Dr. Le Fan from the provincial hospital

16:59.620 --> 17:01.190
for counseling sessions.

17:01.830 --> 17:03.110
You can talk to her

17:03.380 --> 17:04.349
about your thoughts.

17:04.500 --> 17:05.540
She's professional.

17:06.380 --> 17:08.310
Anyway, the school and teachers hope

17:08.589 --> 17:10.349
you'll overcome your problem.

17:12.260 --> 17:13.109
I'm sorry.

17:13.310 --> 17:14.500
It's all right.

17:15.140 --> 17:16.349
Come to me

17:16.349 --> 17:17.619
whenever you're ready.

17:42.230 --> 17:44.350
I can't open up to Dr. Le Fan.

17:45.710 --> 17:47.260
I've got a lot on my mind,

17:48.020 --> 17:49.900
and they're all ugly.

17:51.500 --> 17:53.380
To be honest, I have trouble sleeping.

17:58.350 --> 18:00.140
Is it because of
your parents quarreling?

18:03.950 --> 18:06.380
I don't know
for how long I can go on like this.

18:08.380 --> 18:09.190
Mumu,

18:10.110 --> 18:12.310
once NCEE is over and you leave home,

18:12.350 --> 18:13.860
everything will get better.

18:14.380 --> 18:15.190
But

18:16.620 --> 18:17.660
what about my mom?

18:20.710 --> 18:22.310
What should my mom do?

18:25.470 --> 18:27.910
Yes, I can leave home,

18:28.950 --> 18:31.150
but I'm always their child,

18:31.500 --> 18:33.500
and they're always my parents.

18:33.670 --> 18:35.780
I can leave them and live alone,

18:37.670 --> 18:39.190
but our entangled relationship

18:39.190 --> 18:40.670
will still go on forever.

18:41.260 --> 18:42.630
I can never get rid of it.

18:46.630 --> 18:47.630
Qingyu, that's why

18:48.910 --> 18:49.990
I envy you.

18:50.870 --> 18:51.910
You can endure,

18:53.100 --> 18:54.500
and you're brave enough to leave.

18:55.910 --> 18:59.430
There's light in your heart,

19:00.580 --> 19:03.740
so you're fearless against darkness.

19:07.710 --> 19:08.910
It's not like that, Mumu.

19:10.190 --> 19:12.300
The light inside me was almost gone.

19:13.580 --> 19:14.740
Luckily, I have you.

19:15.580 --> 19:16.710
You saved me.

19:23.020 --> 19:25.870
This is what everyone says about me.

19:26.540 --> 19:27.340
I'm kind,

19:28.260 --> 19:29.060
considerate,

19:29.470 --> 19:30.630
and gentle

19:30.990 --> 19:32.060
as a spring breeze.

19:34.990 --> 19:36.470
Don't you like that?

19:37.060 --> 19:38.950
I don't have much feeling about that.

19:42.100 --> 19:43.100
I just think

19:44.150 --> 19:45.500
that the path ahead of me

19:48.950 --> 19:50.230
feels so dark.

19:50.740 --> 19:52.300
I can't find the light.

19:57.500 --> 19:58.470
Qingyu, that's why

20:00.100 --> 20:01.630
I envy your courage.

20:02.230 --> 20:03.870
At least you can do

20:04.780 --> 20:06.100
what you want to do.

20:15.300 --> 20:16.580
There will be a light for you.

20:36.820 --> 20:38.390
Let's play basketball, rookie.

20:38.540 --> 20:39.430
Sheng isn't here.

20:40.020 --> 20:41.910
Deng Meixi got stuck
on a biology question,

20:41.910 --> 20:44.100
so she and Sheng
went to the library to study.

20:44.230 --> 20:45.100
In the library?

20:45.340 --> 20:46.300
Ming Sheng is something else.

20:46.870 --> 20:47.060
All right.

20:47.060 --> 20:47.740
Next time, then.

20:48.190 --> 20:48.990
Let's go.

20:50.910 --> 20:51.820
Take your things.

20:52.580 --> 20:54.430
Sheng's meeting someone
for karaoke this afternoon.

20:55.020 --> 20:56.020
The prettiest girl
from No. 1 High School?

20:56.630 --> 20:57.430
Let's go.

20:57.990 --> 21:00.060
My buddy tried so many times
to ask her out but failed.

21:01.190 --> 21:03.230
Don't Sheng and the prettiest girl

21:03.340 --> 21:04.820
make an impressive combo?

21:05.020 --> 21:06.300
Are we witnessing a historical moment?

21:06.300 --> 21:07.990
Hurry up. You're never
this expressive in your essays.

21:07.990 --> 21:08.910
Quick.

21:20.300 --> 21:21.230
Are you all right?

21:22.390 --> 21:23.390
It's broken again.

21:24.430 --> 21:25.390
Your dad is unbelievable.

21:25.630 --> 21:26.910
We keep fixing this thing

21:26.990 --> 21:28.230
just to save the money.

21:31.340 --> 21:32.150
Hey.

21:33.150 --> 21:35.780
Isn't that the pretty chick from TV
a few days ago?

21:36.260 --> 21:37.300
Yeah, right.

21:37.430 --> 21:38.780
She's the one who messed up the wedding

21:39.060 --> 21:40.630
mentioned in the forum.

21:41.150 --> 21:41.710
She's pretty.

21:41.710 --> 21:42.260
Let's take a look.

21:42.430 --> 21:43.100
So pretty.

21:44.060 --> 21:44.990
Well, well.

21:45.540 --> 21:46.020
Isn't this

21:46.020 --> 21:48.470
the sister of the prettiest girl
in Shunyun?

21:48.670 --> 21:49.100
Yeah.

21:49.100 --> 21:49.990
You must be mistaken.

21:49.990 --> 21:51.390
How could I be mistaken, madam?

21:51.390 --> 21:53.780
It's you. The owner
of Qiao's Noodle House.

21:53.910 --> 21:54.740
We eat there all the time.

21:54.740 --> 21:55.950
Look, what's happening over there?

21:56.670 --> 21:59.150
How about we have this beauty
join us for a bowl of noodles?

21:59.150 --> 22:00.430
Let go. What are you trying to do?

22:01.150 --> 22:02.260
Isn't that Qiao Qingyu?

22:02.390 --> 22:02.990
Ma'am,

22:03.580 --> 22:05.100
young people like to make friends.

22:05.100 --> 22:06.230
She's not making friends with you.

22:06.230 --> 22:07.190
Let's leave.

22:08.020 --> 22:09.820
What? Are we leaving just like this?

22:25.260 --> 22:26.540
Gosh. How could you

22:27.100 --> 22:27.870
get physical?

22:27.870 --> 22:28.950
Why did you hit me?

22:32.910 --> 22:35.950
Aren't you meeting the prettiest girl
of No.1 High School for karaoke?

22:36.990 --> 22:38.150
What time are we going?

22:38.430 --> 22:39.300
Sing your foot.

22:39.500 --> 22:40.150
What?

22:40.150 --> 22:40.870
Thank you.

22:41.060 --> 22:41.870
We're not meeting her?

22:42.390 --> 22:44.150
Then why did you call us here?

22:44.340 --> 22:46.190
To eat instant noodles
and enjoy the view with you?

22:46.470 --> 22:48.950
I even lied to my dad, saying I had
a study period this evening.

22:49.020 --> 22:50.630
What a letdown.

22:51.190 --> 22:52.060
Just eat.

22:58.150 --> 22:59.150
Sheng.

22:59.820 --> 23:00.990
Why did you pretend
not to know Qiao Qingyu

23:00.990 --> 23:02.340
when you saw her?

23:03.500 --> 23:05.020
Aren't you the kindest one

23:05.020 --> 23:06.060
who always offers help?

23:07.990 --> 23:10.390
Why? Did you fight with her?

23:12.710 --> 23:13.500
Got it.

23:14.190 --> 23:16.630
You're playing hard

23:16.740 --> 23:18.500
to get, right?

23:18.630 --> 23:19.500
Eat your food,

23:19.870 --> 23:21.340
and keep quiet.

23:21.340 --> 23:22.500
Fine, I'll eat.

23:29.350 --> 23:30.630
[The famous Qiao Qingyu spotted.
Gorgeous in her bold outfit]

23:32.020 --> 23:34.060
Here. Read this.

23:39.020 --> 23:39.820
Qiao Qingyu?

23:42.390 --> 23:44.430
"The famous Qiao Qingyu spotted.

23:44.430 --> 23:47.100
Gorgeous in her bold outfit."

23:53.630 --> 23:56.500
DM me for her pictures.

23:56.710 --> 23:57.780
What's this?

24:01.340 --> 24:02.150
Sheng!

24:07.670 --> 24:08.390
Goodness.

24:09.060 --> 24:10.100
This is horrible.

24:10.870 --> 24:12.230
This looks like a crime scene.

24:14.910 --> 24:16.580
Is this Qiao Qingyu's uniform?

24:16.870 --> 24:18.300
Could something have really
happened to her?

24:20.500 --> 24:21.230
Sheng!

24:30.390 --> 24:31.300
Sheng.

24:32.340 --> 24:34.390
Hey, Sheng.

24:35.190 --> 24:36.870
It's just a picture.
Why are you so nervous?

24:40.990 --> 24:41.780
Sheng.

24:49.150 --> 24:49.950
Look.

24:50.190 --> 24:51.260
Is that the one?

24:56.670 --> 24:57.780
Calm down, Sheng.

24:58.910 --> 25:00.230
Sheng...

25:00.470 --> 25:00.820
We're sorry.

25:00.820 --> 25:01.500
What's wrong with you?

25:01.540 --> 25:03.190
- So sorry.
- So sorry.

25:03.670 --> 25:04.740
We're sorry.

25:05.470 --> 25:06.260
Not him.

25:06.390 --> 25:07.190
Not him.

25:08.870 --> 25:10.260
There are a few more
at the signboard of the internet cafe.

25:10.870 --> 25:12.630
Calm down.

25:12.630 --> 25:13.340
"It's you I'm after."

25:13.340 --> 25:14.990
Then she came over and hit you.

25:16.670 --> 25:17.230
What's wrong?

25:17.230 --> 25:19.100
What's your problem?

25:19.100 --> 25:19.630
We can talk this out.

25:19.630 --> 25:20.300
Calm down.

25:20.300 --> 25:21.300
Did you post

25:21.300 --> 25:22.430
Qiao Qingyu's picture?

25:22.430 --> 25:24.020
What does it have to do with you?

25:24.060 --> 25:25.740
Did you post the picture?

25:25.740 --> 25:26.710
Can you just talk properly?

25:26.710 --> 25:27.260
Say it again.

25:27.260 --> 25:28.060
Touch him again if you dare.

25:28.100 --> 25:28.780
Why?

25:28.780 --> 25:29.230
Say it again.

25:29.230 --> 25:29.580
What's wrong?

25:30.060 --> 25:30.870
Come.

25:33.870 --> 25:35.230
Gosh. We're in the soup.

25:39.910 --> 25:40.500
Bring it on.

25:43.670 --> 25:45.100
The picture was edited.

25:45.780 --> 25:47.020
But it's too convincing.

25:49.500 --> 25:51.060
It's all flawed
when you take a closer look.

25:51.470 --> 25:54.060
Here, Qiao Qingyu's face is taken
from the news.

25:54.060 --> 25:55.740
The hair is another layer,

25:55.820 --> 25:57.150
and the background is faked.

25:57.150 --> 25:59.020
[The famous Qiao Qingyu spotted.
Gorgeous in her bold outfit.]

26:04.630 --> 26:05.500
Ye Zilin,

26:06.190 --> 26:06.630
you...

26:07.630 --> 26:08.740
You can't blame me for that.

26:08.990 --> 26:10.150
I didn't even
get to click on the picture

26:10.150 --> 26:11.230
before you ran off.

26:11.260 --> 26:13.300
Don't be mad. It's clear now.

26:13.300 --> 26:15.060
They didn't even get
to touch Qiao Qingyu.

26:15.100 --> 26:16.430
Her mom

26:16.430 --> 26:17.540
scared them off.

26:17.670 --> 26:19.260
It only makes sense
if her mom beat them up.

26:19.580 --> 26:20.580
Now I see why Qiao Qingyu

26:20.580 --> 26:22.020
is so afraid of her mom.

26:22.190 --> 26:24.020
She's tough.

26:25.470 --> 26:26.950
The police arrived quickly, thankfully.

26:28.230 --> 26:29.260
Otherwise, I wouldn't have been able

26:29.260 --> 26:30.150
to handle so many of them

26:30.150 --> 26:30.740
if a fight broke out.

26:30.740 --> 26:31.430
You got so worked up

26:31.430 --> 26:32.100
over a picture.

26:32.780 --> 26:34.540
That's not like you.

26:36.990 --> 26:37.780
Childish.

26:37.870 --> 26:38.740
That's enough.

26:39.390 --> 26:40.390
Can we drop this?

26:40.950 --> 26:41.630
Fine.

26:45.630 --> 26:46.500
Anyway,

26:47.470 --> 26:49.060
the three of us just went through

26:49.780 --> 26:50.710
a life-and-death experience together.

26:53.470 --> 26:54.100
Heh heh.

26:54.500 --> 26:54.740
Good.

26:54.740 --> 26:56.740
But this is serious.

26:56.740 --> 26:57.950
The school will find out.

26:58.060 --> 26:59.260
Both of us are fine,

26:59.390 --> 27:01.100
but you better figure out
how to explain this to your dad.

27:09.740 --> 27:11.190
There's certainly no infection.

27:12.020 --> 27:13.060
But just in case,

27:13.390 --> 27:15.260
so that people
won't keep talking about it.

27:15.540 --> 27:17.230
They're driving me crazy.

27:19.020 --> 27:19.820
Qingyu.

27:21.060 --> 27:21.870
Qingyu?

27:22.390 --> 27:23.990
Let's go to the hospital
tomorrow morning

27:24.540 --> 27:25.340
to get a blood test.

27:27.020 --> 27:30.100
Qingyu has a math test tomorrow.

27:30.950 --> 27:32.710
Missing one test
won't affect her admission.

27:33.100 --> 27:35.870
The school does medical checkups
every term, so there's no need for that.

27:36.260 --> 27:37.990
Don't you get what I'm saying?

27:38.100 --> 27:39.540
The blood test
will put everyone's mind at ease.

27:39.630 --> 27:40.710
If not, they won't stop gossiping.

27:40.710 --> 27:42.340
We've done nothing wrong,
why let them talk?

27:42.430 --> 27:44.430
Just let them be.

27:44.780 --> 27:46.630
At least we know we're clean.

27:46.630 --> 27:48.260
You have no idea
how awful their words are.

27:48.260 --> 27:49.670
They're saying our whole family is sick.

27:51.230 --> 27:53.540
If people see you at the hospital,

27:53.540 --> 27:55.150
won't the rumors just get worse?

27:55.230 --> 27:56.230
You can come, too.

27:58.990 --> 28:00.020
Mom, I'll go.

28:02.580 --> 28:03.820
A blood test is nothing.

28:03.820 --> 28:06.060
It'll be quick.
I'll head straight to school afterward.

28:45.440 --> 28:46.910
Your mom is fast asleep.

28:50.060 --> 28:51.630
She's been like this.

28:51.990 --> 28:53.260
Either she can't sleep,

28:53.470 --> 28:55.190
or can't wake up when she falls asleep.

28:55.260 --> 28:57.910
Well, it's normal when one gets older.

29:01.740 --> 29:03.470
I'll sleep here tonight

29:03.870 --> 29:05.060
so I won't wake her up.

29:18.910 --> 29:20.430
I thought

29:21.390 --> 29:22.990
we got over this.

29:25.100 --> 29:26.710
Somehow, it was brought up again.

29:27.020 --> 29:28.710
Actually,
I didn't want to argue with your mom.

29:30.260 --> 29:32.470
After all, you're sitting for NCEE soon.

29:34.580 --> 29:37.060
Sometimes, when I think about it,
your mom and I are doing quite well.

29:39.780 --> 29:41.300
When we got married,

29:42.300 --> 29:44.100
most people had arranged marriages,

29:44.500 --> 29:45.700
but your mom and I

29:46.150 --> 29:47.670
married for love.

29:51.020 --> 29:54.100
But I don't know

29:54.580 --> 29:56.740
how life turned out this way.

30:01.190 --> 30:02.470
Stop drinking, Dad.

30:11.190 --> 30:14.430
Qingyu, I'm not ashamed
to tell you this.

30:16.500 --> 30:17.470
I'm supposed

30:18.300 --> 30:19.500
to be

30:21.260 --> 30:23.300
the pillar of my family,

30:26.740 --> 30:28.670
but

30:30.470 --> 30:31.910
I often fail.

31:33.230 --> 31:35.430
You guys continue. Take over for me.

31:44.870 --> 31:45.820
Aren't you going to tell Qiao Qingyu

31:46.580 --> 31:48.300
about what happened yesterday?

31:52.340 --> 31:53.470
It has nothing to do with her.

31:56.150 --> 31:57.580
Sheng, your dad is here.

31:57.580 --> 31:58.820
He's in Sun's office.

32:01.740 --> 32:03.300
Too many times, isn't it?

32:05.710 --> 32:08.020
Oh, my.

32:11.470 --> 32:13.060
It seems quite serious.

32:13.780 --> 32:16.630
Sun is scolding your dad so badly.

32:17.340 --> 32:18.190
I asked to meet you

32:18.190 --> 32:19.470
several times, but...

32:19.470 --> 32:21.340
Look at how Sun's talking to your dad.

32:21.820 --> 32:24.190
He's going to chew you out tonight.

32:25.670 --> 32:26.990
You're in for it, Sheng.

32:27.300 --> 32:28.100
Sheng.

32:30.300 --> 32:31.260
Sheng.

32:50.710 --> 32:52.150
Ah, I see you.

32:52.540 --> 32:53.100
Hello.

32:53.100 --> 32:55.470
How's it? Is the signal okay?

32:55.710 --> 32:57.260
It's all right.
The screen isn't lagging.

32:57.780 --> 33:00.340
The performance just ended.

33:00.500 --> 33:01.670
It was a great success.

33:02.430 --> 33:03.990
During the curtain call,

33:03.990 --> 33:05.580
the applause went on

33:06.230 --> 33:07.470
for four or five minutes.

33:07.580 --> 33:09.260
Do you know how thrilled I was?

33:10.470 --> 33:11.300
Oh, by the way,

33:11.780 --> 33:13.060
my fans gave me this.

33:14.950 --> 33:15.630
Mom,

33:16.230 --> 33:17.910
congratulations. Keep up the good work.

33:17.910 --> 33:18.670
Thank you.

33:21.190 --> 33:22.670
You've been drinking this
since you were a kid.

33:22.950 --> 33:24.260
You're quite loyal to it.

33:24.500 --> 33:25.540
What about you? How's everything?

33:25.540 --> 33:26.470
I'm fine.

33:26.670 --> 33:27.670
Today at school,

33:27.670 --> 33:29.500
I made Dr. Ming mad again.

33:30.780 --> 33:31.710
It's a small accomplishment.

33:31.950 --> 33:32.740
Sheng...

33:32.740 --> 33:33.950
Mom, don't persuade me.

33:34.500 --> 33:35.630
I just want to make him angry.

33:36.430 --> 33:37.780
I will never

33:38.540 --> 33:39.430
do as he says.

33:48.260 --> 33:49.260
You've grown up.

33:49.540 --> 33:51.190
We can talk

33:51.190 --> 33:52.260
like adults.

33:52.710 --> 33:54.190
Will you listen to me?

33:54.190 --> 33:54.710
Hmm.

33:54.990 --> 33:56.670
I don't want

33:57.100 --> 33:59.020
you and your dad to be hostile
against each other.

33:59.630 --> 34:01.300
I understand his feelings for you.

34:01.300 --> 34:02.820
He just doesn't know
how to express them.

34:03.580 --> 34:04.430
You can

34:04.990 --> 34:06.430
talk with an open heart

34:06.470 --> 34:07.990
like we do.

34:08.300 --> 34:10.340
It's good for both of you. All right?

34:14.020 --> 34:14.909
Give me a second.

34:27.710 --> 34:28.780
There's something

34:31.820 --> 34:33.739
I've kept inside for over ten years.

34:35.989 --> 34:37.340
I want to tell you now.

34:39.300 --> 34:40.100
Back then...

34:44.580 --> 34:46.469
I was the one who left your dad.

34:59.870 --> 35:01.190
Back then, he was

35:01.190 --> 35:03.820
completely focused on his work.

35:03.820 --> 35:05.430
We quarreled a lot.

35:05.670 --> 35:06.950
I thought if this continued,

35:06.950 --> 35:09.580
it would hurt both of us.

35:11.580 --> 35:12.990
Hence, I insisted on leaving.

35:15.340 --> 35:16.230
Back then,

35:17.740 --> 35:18.670
I was headstrong

35:19.950 --> 35:21.260
and impulsive.

35:22.910 --> 35:24.430
I insisted on taking you with me.

35:27.930 --> 35:29.060
Your grandpa disagreed.

35:30.230 --> 35:31.270
He was right, though.

35:31.870 --> 35:34.540
I was alone in France with no support.

35:35.020 --> 35:36.910
I could barely feed myself.

35:37.470 --> 35:39.350
How could I provide you
with a normal life?

35:46.750 --> 35:49.790
He wanted me to leave

35:52.100 --> 35:53.390
without you.

35:55.950 --> 35:56.950
I was selfish.

35:58.020 --> 35:59.220
Due to that,

36:00.470 --> 36:02.220
your relationship with your dad

36:02.220 --> 36:03.790
ended up like this.

36:09.180 --> 36:10.580
Also, because of my selfishness,

36:11.470 --> 36:13.310
you've become so rebellious.

36:14.310 --> 36:15.990
I don't expect you to forgive me.

36:18.060 --> 36:19.990
I just want you to know the truth.

36:21.020 --> 36:21.910
Sorry.

36:26.950 --> 36:27.700
Sorry.

36:35.910 --> 36:36.540
Yanqiu?

36:44.750 --> 36:46.540
You're taking good care
of Dr. Chen's dog.

36:46.790 --> 36:47.790
You have no idea

36:47.990 --> 36:49.100
how struggled I was

36:49.100 --> 36:50.310
when the dog first came here.

36:50.540 --> 36:52.910
It only started to get on track
after a few days.

36:54.580 --> 36:55.950
Oh, I brought you some fruits.

36:56.580 --> 36:57.580
Thank you.

37:07.020 --> 37:08.540
It's windy today.

37:08.660 --> 37:09.390
Oh, really?

37:14.830 --> 37:16.100
Is everything all right at home?

37:16.350 --> 37:17.140
Yeah.

37:17.430 --> 37:18.220
That's good.

37:22.020 --> 37:23.910
The family of the patient
who passed away

37:23.910 --> 37:25.870
has applied to identify
medical malpractice.

37:26.470 --> 37:28.790
The mediation panel is working on it.

37:28.830 --> 37:30.350
The results will be out in a few days.

37:37.350 --> 37:39.220
Everyone has to
go through the cycle of life.

37:39.700 --> 37:41.990
When they get sick,
they go to the hospital.

37:42.620 --> 37:44.060
If they can't be cured,

37:46.020 --> 37:47.390
it's the doctor's fault.

37:48.430 --> 37:50.220
But doctors aren't miracle workers.

37:50.750 --> 37:52.580
Doctors are treated as innocent targets
for people to vent their anger.

37:52.910 --> 37:54.620
It's unfair to expect so much of them,

37:56.060 --> 37:57.790
but they keep saving lives.

37:57.870 --> 37:58.430
Hmm.

37:59.660 --> 38:02.420
Perhaps this is
what makes our profession

38:02.430 --> 38:04.140
great and sacred.

38:10.950 --> 38:11.750
Everyone

38:13.270 --> 38:15.220
has their own perspective.

38:15.620 --> 38:17.220
They only stand in their own perspective

38:17.220 --> 38:18.060
when assessing a problem.

38:22.270 --> 38:23.180
During this period of time,

38:23.470 --> 38:26.060
I've calmed myself and thought a lot.

38:26.700 --> 38:28.180
About those problems in my life,

38:29.180 --> 38:30.270
I started trying

38:30.310 --> 38:31.700
to see things in the shoes of patients

38:32.430 --> 38:33.470
or even

38:33.750 --> 38:35.430
of my son.

38:37.390 --> 38:38.180
Suddenly,

38:39.140 --> 38:39.990
I understood

38:39.990 --> 38:42.100
why they were so resentful.

38:42.700 --> 38:44.660
When I truly understood them,

38:45.220 --> 38:46.430
my problems

38:46.870 --> 38:48.220
have been resolved as well.

38:49.140 --> 38:50.390
No matter what the result is,

38:50.660 --> 38:51.750
I believe in you.

38:55.340 --> 38:58.500
Don't make it sound so miserable.

38:59.220 --> 39:00.140
It's not that bad.

39:01.390 --> 39:03.430
Even if I can't do surgery anymore,

39:04.270 --> 39:05.100
there are still other things

39:06.180 --> 39:07.660
I can do.

39:08.620 --> 39:10.390
I believe in fairness and justice,

39:10.870 --> 39:11.830
and you.

39:13.540 --> 39:15.500
Enough about me. Let's talk about you.

39:15.790 --> 39:16.950
How are you doing lately?

39:17.500 --> 39:18.140
I...

39:19.020 --> 39:20.220
Madam Zhang

39:20.990 --> 39:22.540
set you up on a blind date, didn't she?

39:22.950 --> 39:25.430
I guess you like him, right?

39:28.660 --> 39:30.830
Yeah, everything goes well.

39:30.830 --> 39:31.500
Good.

39:38.350 --> 39:39.100
I'm warning you.

39:39.100 --> 39:40.750
Don't you dare stare at me!

39:40.990 --> 39:41.750
Chill out.

39:41.750 --> 39:42.950
Are you trying to ruin me?

39:42.950 --> 39:44.220
Please hear me out. Let go.
Talk to us if you want.

39:44.220 --> 39:46.540
I'm your dad.
How dare you call the police on me?

39:46.540 --> 39:48.350
This is a residential area.
Don't make noise here.

39:48.350 --> 39:51.500
Don't arrest me. I must scold her!
I've raised you,

39:51.500 --> 39:52.390
and this is how you treat me?

39:52.390 --> 39:54.180
Please cooperate with us.
Get in the car.

39:58.470 --> 40:00.350
I regret having you!

40:00.350 --> 40:02.500
Please cooperate with us.

40:10.310 --> 40:10.910
Mumu.

40:27.470 --> 40:30.060
Yesterday, I was the one

40:30.750 --> 40:31.750
who called the police.

40:33.990 --> 40:35.270
I wanted to help Mom.

40:36.580 --> 40:38.790
I wanted to be brave for once, like you,

40:39.140 --> 40:40.140
and do something.

40:42.700 --> 40:43.790
The police came

40:43.950 --> 40:45.220
and asked Mom if she wanted to pursue

40:45.220 --> 40:46.620
Dad's responsibility.

40:47.790 --> 40:49.750
She said no without a second thought.

40:51.220 --> 40:52.660
After the police left,

40:54.430 --> 40:56.140
Dad got even angrier

40:56.580 --> 40:58.700
and trashed the house.

40:59.180 --> 41:00.750
Mom said it was my fault

41:01.020 --> 41:02.750
and blamed me for trying to send my dad

41:03.100 --> 41:04.500
to the police station.

41:07.020 --> 41:08.500
I didn't sleep a wink last night.

41:11.060 --> 41:13.020
It's so obvious who's in the wrong.

41:13.470 --> 41:15.390
Is there really no place
to find justice?

41:17.950 --> 41:18.950
The police said

41:19.620 --> 41:21.580
that if it happens again,

41:21.580 --> 41:24.540
we can't let it go.
We need to call them immediately

41:24.540 --> 41:26.100
and seek legal support.

41:29.500 --> 41:30.700
I hate my dad.

41:31.180 --> 41:33.700
I hate that all he does

41:34.350 --> 41:35.910
is hurt me and my mom.

41:39.580 --> 41:40.750
But now,

41:42.750 --> 41:43.910
I hate myself even more.

42:15.450 --> 42:19.140
♪Perhaps♪

42:19.650 --> 42:25.350
♪The more we care,
the more careful we become♪

42:26.490 --> 42:31.890
♪Counting the distance
that separates us♪

42:32.890 --> 42:38.450
♪A single step,
and we'd be closer still♪

42:44.120 --> 42:47.790
♪In the future♪

42:48.250 --> 42:53.970
♪Time will reveal this secret♪

42:55.470 --> 43:00.540
♪Waiting is a silent promise♪

43:01.790 --> 43:06.950
♪That never expires♪

43:10.550 --> 43:15.020
♪Turns out that what's on my mind♪

43:16.020 --> 43:19.690
♪Is your name♪

43:20.190 --> 43:25.290
♪The only stubbornness in my heart♪

43:26.370 --> 43:29.590
♪At first sight♪

43:30.020 --> 43:33.300
♪The future has been determined♪

43:33.990 --> 43:39.550
♪Dreams began to feel real♪

43:40.650 --> 43:44.190
♪Turns out that what's on your mind♪

43:44.650 --> 43:48.590
♪Is a place♪

43:48.890 --> 43:54.450
♪Where the same story is held dear♪

43:55.120 --> 43:58.490
♪Fortunately, I'm not sensible enough♪

43:58.820 --> 44:02.290
♪Courage wasn't late too♪

44:02.820 --> 44:08.890
♪Only then does time not betray
our acquaintance♪
